                <mxCell id="2" value="&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px;margin-top:4px;text-align:center;&quot;&gt;&lt;b&gt;Appointment&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr size=&quot;1&quot;/&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px;margin-left:4px;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;+ bookingCustomerAccount: CustomerAccount&lt;br/&gt;+ visitedPet: Pet&lt;br/&gt;+ hostingStore: Store&lt;br/&gt;+ scheduledDateAndTimeSlot: TimeSlot&lt;br/&gt;+ visitNote: String&lt;br/&gt;+ bookingDate: Date&lt;br/&gt;+ appointmentStatus: String&lt;br/&gt;+ cancellationReason: String&lt;br/&gt;+ checkedInTime: DateTime&lt;br/&gt;+ checkedInBy: Store&lt;br/&gt;+ visitOutcome: VisitOutcome&lt;br/&gt;+ staffVisitNotes: String&lt;br/&gt;+ followUpAction: FollowUpAction&lt;br/&gt;+ followUpDate: Date&lt;br/&gt;+ noShowRecordedBy: Store&lt;br/&gt;+ noShowRecordedAt: DateTime&lt;br/&gt;+ notificationStatus: String&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr size=&quot;1&quot;/&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px;margin-left:4px;font-size:10px;&quot;&gt;+ confirm(): void&lt;br/&gt;+ cancel(cancellation: AppointmentCancellation): void&lt;br/&gt;+ checkIn(checkedInBy: Store): void&lt;br/&gt;+ recordVisitOutcome(outcome: VisitOutcome, staffNotes: String): void&lt;br/&gt;+ recordNoShow(recordedBy: Store): void&lt;br/&gt;+ setFollowUpAction(action: FollowUpAction): void&lt;br/&gt;+ triggerReminder(): void&lt;br/&gt;+ rebook(rebooking: AppointmentRebooking): Appointment&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;hr size=&quot;1&quot;/&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;margin:0px;margin-left:4px;font-size:9px;color:#666;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;must be booked by exactly one customer account; guest checkout cannot book&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;i&gt;must reference exactly one pet&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;i&gt;must reference exactly one store&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;i&gt;must always have a confirmed and booked time slot&lt;/i&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;" style="verticalAlign=top;align=left;overflow=fill;fontSize=12;fontFamily=Helvetica;html=1;whiteSpace=wrap;" vertex="1" parent="1">
